Deprecated. Use IJavaScriptUnit.becomeWorkingCopy(IProgressMonitor) instead. Note that if this deprecated method is used, problems will be reported to the given problem requestor as well as the problem requestor returned by the working copy owner (if not null). While this may be desired in some situations, by and large it is not.
